+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |   Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1)) AS c                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[URL, SearchPhrase], full_filters=[hits.URL LIKE Utf8("%google%"), hits.SearchPhrase != Utf8("")]                                                                                                                                                              |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=sqlite compute_context=memory initial_sql=SELECT `hits`.`SearchPhrase`, min(`hits`.`URL`), count(1) AS `c` FROM `hits` WHERE (`hits`.`URL` LIKE '%google%' AND (`hits`.`SearchPhrase` <> '')) GROUP BY `hits`.`SearchPhrase` ORDER BY `c` DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
